description:
Pestilence, famine, the words and actions of the little horn, political and religious issues all seem to be getting more extreme than ever before. Many feel things are getting worse. But can we put a finger on precisely what is wrong? Are the crises in the world right now what happens at the end? Are we living at the end of time? What does the Bible say about the end of the world? 

This presentation is a review of what happens at the end. How do Bible verses about end-time events demonstrate Gods consistency? Sin and suffering will not be allowed to continue forever, because God finishes what He starts! Learn what you must do to prepare for the end and to follow God alone.
